node.text: Michael Rosen recited his poem and I made the drawing to thank the health care workers over the pandemic. It was shown on the news. Such a privilege to be able to do this.The music is by Max Richter.

node.text: Hello. It’s World Suicide Prevention Day today. It’s a page from the book. I’m drawing for the film today but wanted to post something. I hope you have a good weekend.

node.text: I recently met a wonderful lady who said she reads the book with her grandson. This is their favourite page - so this post is for them.
